oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: 15" rainbow trout caught by man in Cherokee National Forest
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of Currey Turner and the 15" rainbow trout he caught in the Cherokee National Forest. Turner is standing by a body of water wearing a hat and shirt, visible in the photograph. In the background, there is brush and trees.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: RG 82: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
